description: Try our easy to follow Beef & Bean Enchiladas recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Enchilada,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Healthier Easier,Low sugar,Sesame free,Beef,High protein,High fibre,Mince,Tomato,Peanut free
name: Beef & Bean Enchiladas Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a medium saucepan over medium heat. Add garlic and sauté for 1-2 minutes. Add mince, cumin and coriander and cook for 2-3 minutes or until browned.
Stir through the 4 bean mix and Italian tomatoes and continue to cook until thickened. Allow to cool.

Fill wraps with mince mixture, roll up and place into a 1.5L baking dish. Sprinkle with cheese and bake for 20 minutes or until cheese is melted and starting to turn golden. Top enchiladas with lettuce, tomato and coriander to serve.
